                     <interp inst="t17751018-15-person187" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a peruke-maker; I have known the prisoner two years; I never heard any thing amiss of him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17751018-15-person188">
                  Elizabeth
                   Smith
               <interp inst="t17751018-15-person188" type="surname" value="Smith"></interp>
