                  </persName>
            . I keep a public house in Westminster. I have known the prisoner all his life; he was always a very honest industrious man.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17751018-15-person189">
                  William
                   Andrews
               <interp inst="t17751018-15-person189" type="surname" value="Andrews"></interp>
