                     <interp inst="t17751018-15-person189" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a butcher; I have known the prisoner two years; I lived with him three quarters of a year, at Mr. Sewell's in Shoreditch; he bears an exceeding good character.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17751018-15-person190">
